{"type": "article", "id": 24111, "title": "约三个小伙伴，带着这顶 X 型帐篷去野营", "description": "一眼就能看穿的简单设计，还真有人把它做了出来", "date": "2016-03-19T08:00:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5812, "name": "帐篷"}, {"id": 3593, "name": "户外"}, {"id": 16748, "name": "野营"}], "category": 17, "author": 474100, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 373, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702124920Y0miQvptcZfCHKra.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>DOPPELGANGER OUTDOOR 是个日本户外运动品牌，最近他们推出了世界首个 “X” 型的四人帐篷 “<a href=\"http://www.doppelganger-sports.jp/product/t4_85/\">CRAZY X</a>” 。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124913DhY7lEm1gzQWa0Bw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“CRAZY X”之所以 crazy，是因为 DOPPELGANGER OUTDOOR 希望使用者能够像孩子一样愉快地在野外玩乐，找回孩童时代那种打造“秘密基地”的感觉。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124914x8udkgljIyRbFA9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这个帐篷的外观设计一点都不复杂，钻进去之后每人都有属于自己的空间，但是高度很低，连坐都不能坐。无聊的时候大家可以聚在中心打打牌，甚至有网友说可以趴着打会儿麻将。请想象所有人聚在一起时，是否像突然没有了距离感一样，重返那些小伙伴们凑在一块聊天扯淡的年轻时光？<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124914em3XMNcF1ZG7qCKa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124915LiwFr3Dn2MBCWTUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124915sywjCrHxTWp39Dk1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">通风口</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当然缺点也一目了然，尽管帐篷设置了好几处通风口，仍然会受到一些不可控因素的影响。不过比起朋友们在一起玩耍的快乐，这种小小的不适也不算什么。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124916DCWhmw6NExKkfgFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">顶部镂空</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021249171NitZ8CAyUB7FX9W.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">夜晚时打开电灯</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">另外和普通的帐篷构造相比，由于整体高度很矮，所以不易受强风影响，防水性和耐压性较强。在中央可以透过顶部的网眼欣赏夜空，重量只有 3.6 千克。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124917OluZhQSLGNFxk7ow.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">还有单人版的睡袋帐篷</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>DOPPELGANGER OUTDOOR 的经营范围包括帐篷、睡袋、手杖、照明灯、雪鞋、烧烤架等等，但他们生产的商品都稍微有些“特别”。这个被叫做<a href=\"http://www.doppelganger-sports.jp/product/q1_261_262/\">单身狗烧烤架</a>的东西你可能见过，它能折叠成普通斜挎包的大小，展开后变成带底座的烧烤架。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124918xnU9SRAsfghX4tew.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702124919i8EMgdV1cv0h2Iux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">再配上炭盆、篦子、烧烤夹，一次能刚好烤几块肉和蔬菜，保证一个人的饭量，也是专为那些想自己配着春光享用露天美食的人设计。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 <a href=\"http://www.doppelganger-sports.jp/\">doppelganger</a></p>\n\n"}